(a)5 U.S.C. 765.Sept. 7, 1916, ch. 458, § 15, 39 Stat. 746. 5 U.S.C. 766.Sept. 7, 1916, ch. 458, § 16, 39 Stat. 746. (b)5 U.S.C. 767.Sept. 7, 1916, ch. 458, § 17, 39 Stat. 746.
Subsection (b)(2) is added on authority of former section 770, which is carried into section 8122, to complete the coverage of this section. Administration of this subchapter was transferred to the Secretary of Labor by section 1 of 1950 Reorg. Plan No. 19, 64 Stat. 1271 (see section 8145). Standard changes are made to conform with the definitions applicable and the style of this title as outlined in the preface to the report.
